      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API \n\n// upload a video\n\nPOST /videos\n{\n    Video,\n    VideoMetadata\n}\n\n\n// watch a video\nGET /videos/{videoID} -> Video & VideoMetada",
